{"tid":2189850,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭松泰：四年前選舉開票那個晚上，是顛覆了我對本港爭取民主的看法，但我不會公開評論，大家明嘅就明。共勉之。","createTime":"2020-09-05T07:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T09:53:28.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e972903702ae1c9144736584321f5c1f47150d29","tid":2189850,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:32:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ypWz6yw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FypWz6yw.jpg&h=606522d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭松泰：<br />\n當大家在回顧四年前選舉開票的一刻、這些年來的心情，以及經歷動盪的感想等；這個周末我們如常擺街站宣揚熱血的理念，一直深耕細作，做好公民教育。<br />\n四年前的那個晚上，是顛覆了我對本港爭取民主的看法，但我不會公開評論，大家明嘅就明。共勉之。"},{"pid":"9dbb1a44e74f3285526263a5eb0642da8cf7bb38","tid":2189850,"uid":121450,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:33:34.000Z","msg":"大家明嘅就明?<br />\n<br />\n講嘢咁似 葉國謙，阿爺心裏有數style"},{"pid":"84d85c95a2b4a5b40f9ca2fd4248de4ca22d1fa4","tid":2189850,"uid":131282,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:34:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04de69699047a134cd662752731d15a19396fe71","tid":2189850,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:39:25.000Z","msg":"又屌票。"},{"pid":"92dc9fcdaeb2485099678e92892a45a78a24e0c2","tid":2189850,"uid":4460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:40:13.000Z","msg":"收皮死撚開"},{"pid":"1d190eafe59be2b9e378ab0048812b746b801809","tid":2189850,"uid":38518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:41:24.000Z","msg":"快撚啲死啦"},{"pid":"e08a93d3c063b2b5eb87ca26ec93310f7898da92","tid":2189850,"uid":144541,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"84d85c95a2b4a5b40f9ca2fd4248de4ca22d1fa4","tid":2189850,"uid":131282,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:34:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:42:24.000Z","msg":"泛登仔點駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/w